---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import QuickSummary from '../components/QuickSummary.astro';
---

<Layout title="Heroes" description="Hero rarity, vehicle types, and when to transition away from SSR heroes in Last War: Survival.">
  <h1>Heroes</h1>

  <QuickSummary>
    <p>SR = early filler. SSR = strong mid-game workhorses (some promotable to UR). UR = long-term investment. Focus on mono-type teams.</p>
  </QuickSummary>

  <h2>Vehicle Types</h2>
  <p>Tank, Aircraft, and Missile follow a counter cycle. Always build mono-type squads for the significant type bonus.</p>

  <h2>When to Stop Using SSR Heroes</h2>
  <p>Keep your highest-starred SSR/promotable heroes in your main squad until you have UR replacements at comparable investment. A 5-star SSR is usually better than a 2-star UR for mid-game content.</p>
  <p>Promotable SSRs (Mason, Scarlett, etc. per season) are worth extra investment because they become UR.</p>
</Layout>